* Ruck, Carl A.P. and Danny Staples, &quot;The World of Classical Myth&quot; 1994, p. 26 et seq. 
* Wright, F. A., &quot;The Food of the Gods&quot;, &quot;The Classical Review&quot; 31.1, (February 1917:4–6).

