* &quot;Alnus vilmoriana&quot; 
* &quot;Alnus washingtonia&quot; 
==== Hybrids ====
The following hybrids have been described:
* &quot;Alnus × elliptica&quot; (&quot;A. cordata&quot; × &quot;A. glutinosa&quot;)
* &quot;Alnus × fallacina&quot; (&quot;A. incana&quot; subsp. &quot;rugosa&quot; × &quot;A. serrulata&quot;)
* &quot;Alnus × hanedae&quot; (&quot;A. firma&quot; × &quot;A. sieboldiana&quot;)
* &quot;Alnus × hosoii&quot; (&quot;A. maximowiczii&quot; × &quot;A. pendula&quot;)
